latestPosts.caption:
My favourite Australian small fashion businesses: what they make and their size range ✨

1. @itadaki.store - androgynous streetwear with lots of plaid pieces 
Sizes = 6-14

2. @katharinalouu - feminine clothing & swimwear (plaid & patterns)
Sizes = 6-18

3. @eeyo.shop - dopamine inducing, colourful tops 
Sizes = 6-18 

4. @ramptramptrampstamp - thoughtful luxury 
Sizes = 6-20+ (depending on the piece) 

5. @_karlaidlaw - unique streetwear with lots of patterns and textures 
Sizes = 6-18 

6. @cakeysportsman - creative and artistic RTW with the most incredible avant-garde shoes 
Sizes = 6-16

7. @bonniee_the_brand - handmade casual to evening tops with buttons and sequins, as well as denim and flowy skirts 
Sizes = made to order 

8. @maroskepeech - demi belts, leggings and leotards 
Sizes ‎ = 4-16

9. @apresstudio_ - modern, relaxed and refined patterned pieces 
Sizes ‎ = 4-20

10. @monphell - exaggerated proportions and sculptural silhouettes. Unisex suits and streetwear 
Sizes ‎ = many items are ‘one size’, others range from 8-12

11. @modemischiefstudios - feminine, contemporary streetwear. Blouses, dresses, skirts and more
Sizes ‎ = vary depending on style. 4-16

12. @sage.avenue - elevated essentials and stunning bags
Sizes ‎ = 6-12

13. @unreal_fur - faux fur clothing and vegan outerwear and accessories 
Sizes ‎ = 6-14

14. @jaggernautjewellery - authentic jewellery handpicked from India
Sizes ‎ = vary depending on piece 

15. @studiokatiegray - consciously crafted romantic pieces. 
Sizes ‎ = vary depending on piece. 6-14

16. @milliesavage_ - handcrafted and custom, vibrant and bold jewellery
Sizes = vary depending on piece (made to order too)

17. @dzo__ - romantic ready to wear and made to order pieces 
Sizes ‎ = made to order, ready to ship 6-14

18. @odysseusandpenelope_ - colourful swimwear, resort and elevated basics 
Sizes ‎ = 6-16

19. @knitwithelabel - handmade elevated pieces with lace and patterns 
Sizes = 6-20 

#fashioninspo #wheretoshop #australiansmallbusiness #fashioninfluencer #outfitideas #outfitinspo
